                                                                                                                                Containers and layout

                                                                                                                                Sheet

                                                                                                                                Partially stable

                                                                                                                                Sheets allow users to interact with two surfaces simultaneously. In Uber apps, sheets are often used to display related information, like location results, on top of a map.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Content
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                Metrics

                                                                                                                                Sheet header

                                                                                                                                Sheet header without action
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                A simple sheet header with only a title and/or description can be as wide as the screen with 16 padding on each side.

                                                                                                                                Sheet header with actions
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Action buttons are 8 away from the edge of the screen. Since tertiary buttons don't have a background, text can extend all the way to the button while still having a visual space between the text and the icons.

                                                                                                                                Sheet

                                                                                                                                Draggable sheet (2 states)
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "Sheet height controller, Button, Half screen. Double-tap to toggle.”

                                                                                                                                Title: Sheet height controller

                                                                                                                                Value: Half screen | Fullscreen

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Hint: Double-tap to toggle


                                                                                                                                Announcement:

                                                                                                                                Double-tapping should announce the new value and nothing else. For example, “Sheet height controller, fullscreen.”


                                                                                                                                ﻿Notes:

                                                                                                                                If the sheet only supports 2 states, this control should toggle between them. The combo of states could be

                                                                                                                                1) Half screen | Full screen

                                                                                                                                2) Full screen | Half screen


                                                                                                                                Support 3 finger scroll gesture for content in the sheet

                                                                                                                                Draggable sheet (3 states)
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "Sheet height controller, Half screen, Button. Adjust the size of the sheet overlaying the map. Custom actions available.”

                                                                                                                                Title: Sheet height controller

                                                                                                                                Value: Minimized | Half-screen | Full-screen

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Hint: Adjust the size of the sheet overlaying the map.


                                                                                                                                Custom actions:

                                                                                                                                Expand

                                                                                                                                Collapse

                                                                                                                                Activate default


                                                                                                                                Notes:

                                                                                                                                • Support 3 finger scroll gesture for content in the sheet
                                                                                                                                • Double-tapping controller should cycle through the 3 states.
                                                                                                                                • Double-tapping an action in the custom actions should announce the new value (state) of the sheet and nothing else. For example, “Sheet height controller, full-screen.”

                                                                                                                                Sheet

                                                                                                                                Draggable sheet (2 states)
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced previewed:

                                                                                                                                "Sheet height controller, Half screen, Button, Double-tap to adjust the size of the sheet overlaying the map.”

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: Sheet height controller.

                                                                                                                                Value/StateDescription: Half screen | Expanded

                                                                                                                                Role: Button

                                                                                                                                Action: Double-tap to adjust the size of the sheet overlaying the map.


                                                                                                                                If the sheet only supports 2 states, this control should toggle between them.

                                                                                                                                1. Half screen | Expanded

                                                                                                                                2. Expanded | Half screen

                                                                                                                                Draggable sheet (3 states)
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced previewed:

                                                                                                                                "Sheet height controller, Half screen, Button, Double-tap to adjust the screen size overlaying the map.”

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: Sheet height controller.

                                                                                                                                Value/StateDescription: Half screen | Expanded | Collapsed

                                                                                                                                Role: Button

                                                                                                                                Action: Double-tap to adjust the screen size that is overlaying the map.


                                                                                                                                The combo of states could be:

                                                                                                                                1. Half screen | Expanded

                                                                                                                                2. Expanded | Collapsed

                                                                                                                                3. Collapsed | Half screen
